Thanks so much, Steve.

00:05:30.320 --> 00:05:31.720
It's really an honor to be here.

00:05:31.720 --> 00:05:33.560
So I should just
mention, Global Lives

00:05:33.560 --> 00:05:36.620
was founded just a few months
