00:12:57.670 --> 00:12:59.190
-The Global Lives
Project set out

00:12:59.190 --> 00:13:02.010
to document 24 hours
in the daily life

00:13:02.010 --> 00:13:04.260
of 10 people who
roughly represent

00:13:04.260 --> 00:13:08.002
the diversity of humanity.

00:13:08.002 --> 00:13:10.736
-From the most intimate to
the most mundane moments,

00:13:10.736 --> 00:13:13.445
