00:13:33.140 --> 00:13:36.000
-We also learned that more than
half the world lives in cities.

00:13:36.000 --> 00:13:39.300
So we chose five urban
and five rural people.

00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:40.830
-Income.

00:13:40.830 --> 00:13:43.230
We conducted detailed
economic research

00:13:43.230 --> 00:13:46.360
to select 10 people whose
earnings roughly represent

00:13:46.360 --> 00:13:48.800
global income distribution.

00:13:48.800 --> 00:13:49.533
-Gender.

00:13:49.533 --> 00:13:50.240
Half men.

00:13:50.240 --> 00:13:52.500
Half women.

00:13:52.500 --> 00:13:54.400
-Religion.

00:13:54.400 --> 00:13:58.960
The actual religious
distribution of the planet.

00:13:58.960 --> 00:14:00.142
-Age.

00:14:00.142 --> 00:14:02.730
The actual age
distribution of the planet.

00:14:02.730 --> 00:14:06.976
