00:39:02.730 --> 00:39:04.420
And that's really
fascinating to me.

00:39:04.420 --> 00:39:07.402
And I think from our
culture, we often

00:39:07.402 --> 00:39:09.110
tend to have this sort
of savior complex,

00:39:09.110 --> 00:39:11.360
like, how can I help you.

00:39:11.360 --> 00:39:15.330
And I'm curious to know
what out of this project

00:39:15.330 --> 00:39:18.031
