is around inequality, with
Barack Obama talking more

00:46:32.290 --> 00:46:33.930
and more about
inequality, I think

00:46:33.930 --> 00:46:35.580
that's a conversation
increasingly

00:46:35.580 --> 00:46:38.040
we're ready to have as a globe.

00:46:38.040 --> 00:46:42.030
But I think it's still a
really important challenge.

00:46:42.030 --> 00:46:43.870
And I hope that
Global Lives provokes

00:46:43.870 --> 00:46:47.000
